cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE 

This paper presents a tactile sensor for a robot skin, which is relevant to the field of robotics (cs.RO). The sensor uses a color camera and machine learning techniques for contact localization, which involves computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of classical machine learning techniques, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and neural networks (cs.NE).
